# DevSecOps Chain

| Step | k8s-forge module | Purpose |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Code | Kubernetes raw / Helm | Describe the application in `app.yaml` and render local assets |
| Build | CI GitHub Actions | Prepare Python build and package checks |
| Test | CI GitHub Actions | Prepare linting, typing, and test workflows |
| Scan | Supply Chain / CI / Security Audit | Prepare vulnerability, SBOM, and hardening review workflows |
| Package | Helm | Package Kubernetes intent as a local chart |
| Deploy | Kubernetes raw / Helm / GitOps | Generate assets that can later feed manual or GitOps delivery |
| Observe | Observability | Prepare metrics scraping and dashboard review |
| Trace | Tracing | Prepare OpenTelemetry and Tempo examples |
| Secure | NetworkPolicy / Kyverno / Security Audit | Prepare network, admission, and hardening controls |
| Audit | Security Audit | Produce local security review and checklist |
| Document | Capstone | Produce final lab synthesis and `v1.0.0 readiness` notes |

Every step remains readiness-oriented. The Capstone records the chain; it does not execute the chain.
